CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 21, 1946, pg. 8, reads: "PRESIDENT OF SHOP OWNERS - Mrs. Rose Johnson of Pittsburgh is the president of the Beauty Shop Owners of Pennsylvania, Inc., which will hold its first annual conclave Oct. 6-8. Mrs. Johnson has sent out a call for all shop owners, operators and beauticians to join in this event which will bind all beauticians closer in common bond. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Rose Johnson, president of Beauty Shop Owners of Pennsylvania, Inc., wearing floral dress, and holding telephone to ear, in Harris Studio with parted dark curtain on right
